  "originalContent": "<div class=\"article_body\">\ndsr面试分为两个rounds，第一个round两轮(stats + data intuition)，pass才会约第二个round的三轮（data intuition + programming + bq）<br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n体验非常非常好的面试，尽管题目没有全部答完美，但是两轮面试官都非常有耐心会引导，在提示下找到答案。<div id=\"1p3a-ad-thread-paragraph\" style=\"margin-top:20px;margin-bottom:20px\"></div><br/>\n<br/>\n<div class=\"locked\">以下内容需要积分高于 188 您已经可以浏览</div><br/>\n<div style=\"border:1px solid #C2D5E3;padding:8px 8px 8px 24px\">stat<ul class=\"litype_1\" type=\"1\"><li>test population mean, meaning of p-value = x% in this context</li><li>for pop mean, construct 95% CI = [a, b] based on sample mean, s.e. = 0.1, x_bar = 1, how to ensure s.e. = .01? followup: what if sample size cannot change?</li><li>suppose we have a sample X_1, X_2, … X_n ~ X. how to estimate P(X&gt;10)? how to construct 95% CI for P(X&gt;10)? interpret 95% CI = [a, b] in terms of p = P(X &gt; 10)?<br/>\n</li></ul><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\ndata intuition<ul class=\"litype_1\" type=\"1\"><li>explain bias-variance tradeoff. what to do if model is better on training than test?</li><li>start with 1000 features, how to estimate conversion rate?</li><li>X ~ N(mu, <a class=\"relatedlink\" href=\"https://link.1point3acres.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fs%3Fk%3DSigma\" target=\"_blank\">sigma</a>^2), can observe Y ~ X when X &gt; 3. estimate mu, sigma^2. followup: how to construct 95% CI for mu, sigma^2？<br/>\n</li></ul></div><br/>\n<span style=\"display:none\"></span><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n两轮都是许多minor detail followups，每一步都需要解释清楚为什么，对数理统计基础要求很高，建议大家复习巩固基础知识。求加米看面经，祝大家面试顺利offer多多！\n<div class=\"lg:w-550px bg-#fafafa p-6 mt-8 mx-auto\">\n<div class=\"flex\">\n<div class=\"w-24 text-center\">\n<a href=\"https://jobs.1point3acres.com/companies/google\" target=\"_blank\">\n<img class=\"w-full\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\"/>\n<div class=\"mt-2 text-base font-bold\">Google</div>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://jobs.1point3acres.com/companies/google/review\" target=\"_blank\">\n<div class=\"flex item